u_x\cos\theta+u_y\sin\theta=u_r,
-u_xr\sin\theta+u_yr\cos\theta=u_\theta.
u_x=u_r\cos\theta-u_\theta\frac{\sin\theta}{r}\quad\text{ and }\quad u_y=u_r\sin\theta+u_\theta\frac{\cos\theta}{r}.
